{"tid":1872210,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳茂波：武漢肺炎迅速向全國蔓延 對內地經濟影響大","createTime":"2020-02-10T03:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T04:56:37.000Z","uid":144372,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6af3adca653eac1c6087b631c8bc6a74e34f8ff5","tid":1872210,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E6%96%99%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E8%B6%85%E6%B2%99%E5%A3%AB-214500432.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%258C%25AB%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25A3%25AB-214500432.html&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=24f58f74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E6%96%99%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E8%B6%85%E6%B2%99%E5%A3%AB-214500432.html</a><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波於網誌撰文指，在疫情蔓延前，香港已面對頗為嚴峻的經濟環境，去年第四季的本地生產總值出現負增長及零售銷貨量急跌。目前內地旅客佔整體訪港旅客人數的七成八，比率遠高於○二年的四成一。而近年旅遊業佔香港總服務輸出三成二，高於沙士時期的兩成一。旅客銳減，飲食、零售、消費及旅遊相關等行業將受到重創，令香港就業市場面對的壓力將增大，他預期最新的失業率數字，很大機會高於去年第四季的百分之三點三。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳指疫情迅速向全國蔓延，對於正在轉型的內地經濟，造成的影響亦會比沙士時期更大。若中國經濟增長的動力放慢，全球的經濟增長亦會受到影響。"},{"pid":"16a8aff34d5350481a44e2666ca6c88a2df551c4","tid":1872210,"uid":1430,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19f2f5c7b7af8e28db5ba225030e01e1e6d7380","tid":1872210,"uid":1903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16a8aff34d5350481a44e2666ca6c88a2df551c4","tid":1872210,"uid":1430,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"關我撚事<img src=\"/assets